casebody.data:
No. 10-9370. Anthony E. Lewis, Petitioner v. Washington. 563 U.S. 933, 131 S. Ct. 2120,

179 L. Ed. 2d 887,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 2947. April 18, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Washington, Division 1, dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
